Symbol.Script_UI:
! ============================================================================== ! ========== Strings for Localization ! ==============================================================================
strUiDialogTitle = "" strUiPageTitle = `Warning!` if BO_prodaturl <> "" then strProductLink = "http://" + BO_prodaturl else strProductLink = "" endif
strLinktoManufact = `Link to Manufacturer`
strErr1 = `The Macro Library which is necessary for this Object is not loaded as Active Library.` strErr2 = `The loaded Macro Library is older than needed.` strErr3 = `The loaded Macro Library is newer than needed.` strErr4 = `Please use the newest Object!` strErr5 = `Please load the most up-to-date Macro Library as Active Library by Library Manager!` strErr6 = `Don't forget to remove the old Macro Library from the Active Libraries!` strErr7 = `The language of the object and the Macro Library are different.` strErr8 = `Please load the same language version of the Macro Library!`
uiStrError = "" uiStrDownloadMacroLib = "" if iLibError = LIBERR_MISSING then ! missing macro library uiStrError = strErr1 + "\n" + strErr5 endif if iLibError = LIBERR_OLDMACRO then ! old macro library uiStrError = strErr2 + "\n" + strErr5 + "\n" + strErr6 endif if iLibError = LIBERR_OLDOBJECT then ! old object uiStrError = strErr3 + "\n" + strErr4 uiStrDownloadMacroLib = `Download the newest Object` else uiStrDownloadMacroLib = `Download the most up-to-date Macro Library` endif if iLibError = LIBERR_DIFFLANG then ! different languages uiStrError = strErr7 + "\n" + strErr8 endif
! ============================================================================== ! ============================================================================== if abs (iLibError) > eps then xCompLogo = 1 yCompLogo = 1 hCompLogo = 30 ! logo height on UI ! TODO wCompLogo = (70/35) * hCompLogo ! real (width/height) of the logo file (pixel) ! TODO dStartSep = 61
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ui_dialog strUiDialogTitle
ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page ui_page gs_ui_current_page, -1, strUiPageTitle, "menu_icon_alert_ac20"
ui_separator dStartSep, 29, 443, 29
! ui_pict "company_logo", xCompLogo, yCompLogo, wCompLogo, hCompLogo, 1
nameAC = "" qq = request ("name_of_program", "", nameAC) isWin = (strstr (nameAC, ".exe") or strstr (nameAC, ".EXE")) ui_pict_button ui_link, strLinktoManufact, "", 282, 2 * isWin, 161, 25 - 4 * isWin, 0, BO_brandurl ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ui_pict "ui_exclamation_mark(2)_30x93", 1, 36, 30, 93, 1 ui_pict "ui_exclamation_mark(2)_30x93", 412, 36, 30, 93, 1
ui_style 0, 1 ui_outfield uiStrError, 33, 36, 378, 66, 2
ui_pict_button ui_link, uiStrDownloadMacroLib, "", 33, 105, 378, 22, 0, strProductLink ui_style 0, 0
ui_separator 1, 132, 442, 132
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
strBIMobject = `To download more high quality objects please visit us at bimobject.com` strWantToGet = `Want to get more out of your BIM objects?` strDownloadApp = `Download our ArchiCAD app now!`
! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
wLogo = 169 xLogo = (444 - wLogo) / 2 yLogo = 137
nIcon = 5 dIcon = 18 wIcon = 32 hIcon = wIcon xIcon = (444 - nIcon * wIcon - (nIcon - 1) * dIcon) / 2 yIcon = yLogo + 76 dx = wIcon + dIcon wDLButton = nIcon * wIcon + (nIcon - 1) * dIcon
uilink_bimobject = "http://www.bimobject.com" uilink_bo_facebook = "https://www.facebook.com/BIMobject" uilink_bo_youtube = "https://www.youtube.com/user/BIMobject/videos" uilink_bo_twitter = "https://twitter.com/BIMobject" uilink_bo_linkedin = "https://www.linkedin.com/company/bimobject" uilink_bo_app = "http://info.bimobject.com/archicad-app"
yy = yLogo ui_pict "bimobject_logo_info", xLogo, yy, 169, 30, 1 yy = yy + 33
ui_outfield strWantToGet, 0, yy, 444, 14, 2 yy = yy + 18
ui_button ui_link, strDownloadApp, xIcon, yy, wDLButton, 16, 0, uilink_bo_app yy = yy + 42
xx = xIcon ui_pict_button ui_link, "", "ui_icon_website", xx, yIcon, wIcon, hIcon, 0, uilink_bimobject xx = xx + dx ui_pict_button ui_link, "", "ui_icon_facebook", xx, yIcon, wIcon, hIcon, 0, uilink_bo_facebook xx = xx + dx ui_pict_button ui_link, "", "ui_icon_youtube", xx, yIcon, wIcon, hIcon, 0, uilink_bo_youtube xx = xx + dx ui_pict_button ui_link, "", "ui_icon_twitter", xx, yIcon, wIcon, hIcon, 0, uilink_bo_twitter xx = xx + dx ui_pict_button ui_link, "", "ui_icon_linkedin", xx, yIcon, wIcon, hIcon, 0, uilink_bo_linkedin
ui_outfield strBIMobject, 0, 250, 444, 14, 2 endif
! ============================================================================== ! ============ END ============ END ============ END ============ END ========== ! ==============================================================================
end
! ============================================================================== ! ============ END ============ END ============ END ============ END ========== ! ==============================================================================
